 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search SAP HRIT Project Manager (13799) Baer Group Wilmington, DE Remote The Baer Group is looking for SAP HRIT Project Manager for a 12 month Remote project. 
 Title:  SAP HRIT Project Manager 
 Location:  Remote (Must be based in US) 
 Duration:  12 months 
 Rate:  All-Inclusive 
 
 Project Background: 
 Our client is in the early stages of building a project team to work on a divestiture program which will require creating a new SAP ECC instance to migrate both master and historical transaction data and provide an ongoing foundation to support future business operations. The scope of the program will include all FIN, HCM, and SCM related content, underlying BW reporting structures and introduction of a new SAP HANA data foundation. 
 Requirements: 
 Delivery and PM experience with SAP Core HR 
 
 Company Overview: 
 The Baer Group is an Enterprise Technology Consulting firm based in Atlanta, GA providing job opportunities with several 1st Tier Global Systems Integrators and a wide array of Fortune 1000 clients. Consultants and Employees of TBG enjoy access to the highest profile job opportunities across leading Enterprise Technology Solutions ranging from Digital Transformation programs utilizing the latest technologies from SAP and Oracle to a wide range of emerging Cloud based infrastructure, application and AI related solutions.
